@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics

### GET available vehicles
GET {{baseUrl}}/Vehicles?$filter=status eq 'Available'

### GET shipments filtered by status InTransit
GET {{baseUrl}}/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'InTransit'

### GET all shipments for a specific customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/Shipments?$filter=customer_ID eq e1111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

### POST a new shipment booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber":"SL-2026-99999",
  "customer":{
    "ID":"e1111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
  },
  "driver":{
    "ID":"aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa"
  },
  "vehicle":{
    "ID":"11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
  },
  "pickupAddress":"Whitefield",
  "deliveryAddress":"Electronic City",
  "pickupCity":"Bangalore",
  "deliveryCity":"Bangalore",
  "weight":100,
  "bookedAt":"2026-06-01T10:00:00Z",
  "estimatedDelivery":"2026-06-02",
  "actualDistance":35,
  "charges":1200
}

### PATCH shipment status to Delivered
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/Shipments(22222222-bbbb-2222-bbbb-222222222222)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status":"Delivered",
  "deliveredAt":"2026-06-02T18:00:00Z"
}

### GET routes between two cities
GET {{baseUrl}}/Routes?$filter=fromCity eq 'Bangalore' and toCity eq 'Chennai'

### GET drivers sorted by rating descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/Drivers?$orderby=rating desc

